{
  "text": "Proper tumor tissue homing of infused NK cells is a prerequisite for their ability to induce tumor regression. However, studies characterizing the in vivo migration capacity of adoptively infused NK cells have been largely overlooked [CITATION_1] ",
  "correct_citation": {
